column5: Just got back from Minaki. Fishing was great a lot of 20"+ walleyes the biggest was 29". There was 13 in our group and there were 7 Muskies caught from 32" to 42". Would like to thank the guys from South Dakota for helping us find the big walleyes.
I'll be going up there mid August.Will be mostly jigging for walleyes when not musky fishing.What colors work best there?Thanks
